# web-change-checker
# 
# configuration file, contains one site to watch on each line
# format of a line is:
#   site;striphtml;email;email;...
#
# where
#   'site' is a valid URL to be watched for updates
#   'striphtml' determines (if "yes") that common html entities should be replaced by ascii
#   'email' is any valid mail adress to be notified on change
